Requirements:
	* Python
	* python-twitter: http://code.google.com/p/python-twitter/
	* python-twitter patch for native retweet:
		http://code.google.com/p/python-twitter/issues/detail?id=130
	* python-twitter patch for new API:
		http://code.google.com/p/python-twitter/issues/detail?id=152

Setup:
	* Edit the config and API sections in bot.py

Run:
	* Execute: python bot.py

